sys_remote_update_set.description:
@Author: Frank Schuster & Matt Metten (ServiceNow)
@Release Date: May 7th, 2017
@Content:
- Contains 3 new tables: Service Portal Announcement & Announcement Views + a new Instance table for the Header Announcement Widget
- Added 4 new widgets: Announcement Overview, Announcement Picker, Announcements for Header, Announcement Detail View
- The Header widget can be embedded into your own Portal header (Example included: look for the Header "Stock Header with Announcements")
- Announcement Header Widget relies heavily on the Instance options. As this is not dragged and dropped onto a page, the instance was manually created - look for the Widget Instance with the ID "announcement-header-instance"
- Only Published Announcements will be shown in the portals, where the header includes the announcement widget
- Record Watcher on the Header widget to update announcements in real-time. Event will be broadcasted to all other announcement widgets.
